    Stamp
    A model class used to define simple graphics options to be applied to JLabel or JButtons @see javax.swing.JLabel @see javax.swing.JButton There are two characteristics that are manipulated by stamps: - The JLabel or JButton's border - The JLabel's or JButton's text The border is defined by an integer value that is a multiple of some combination of the first four prime numbers 2,3,5,7 (1 is not considered a prime).
